name: Ten Numb (V)
Lore: 'Sullustan gunner. Pilot of Blue 5. Ordered to head a B-wing attack against Imperial command ships at the Battle Of Endor.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Rogue Squadron Pilot. While piloting a B-Wing or X-Wing, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and during battle (unless Outrider on table), may reduce the power of one opponent''s starfighter at same system by 4.',
